63
00:02:22,611 --> 00:02:24,672
Making menus, beating bugs, exploring the edges

64
00:02:24,672 --> 00:02:26,392
of your design, and then wrapping it all up

65
00:02:26,392 --> 00:02:27,872
in a play-tested package.

66
00:02:27,872 --> 00:02:31,933
